title: Doctor.Who.2005.S05E13.The.Big.Bang.fanedit.avi
description: This is Doctor Who, S05E13, The Big Bang. I removed the short flashbacks in the museum when The Doctor goes back in time to Rory and little Amy. I just wondered what it would be like without them. I think it works. The flashbacks were just to remind you of what you already saw. I think it's more fun to see the events from the different timeframes instead of jumping back and forth. Anyway, try it if you want. Enjoy.
